7. Vienna, 4505. ff. 1-29. Cited as C.

On paper. 4to. Handwriting of the first half of the 15th century. With catchwords resembling those of 3930, and with the glosses of 4302, but placed in the text and supplemented by others, some of which are in Bohemian. Contents (including the Appendix) as in 1387.
